text: Tingupidae is a family of millipedes in the order Chordeumatida. There are at least 3 genera and about 14 described species in Tingupidae. ==Genera== * Blancosoma Shear & Hubbard, 1998 * Buotus Chamberlin, 1940 * Tingupa Chamberlin, 1910 ==References== ==Further reading== * * * * Category:Chordeumatida Category:Millipede families
